         </seg> the wind that blew me from <lb n="c57-0131__main__3"/>the detested shore of <seg xml:id="C27_app1040-fMS">Ireland</seg> and the sea <lb n="c57-0131__main__4"/>which surrounded <seg xml:id="C27_app1042-fMS">me</seg> told me too <w ana="start"/>forci<lb n="c57-0131__main__5"/>bly<w ana="end"/> that I was deceived by no <seg xml:id="C27_app1044-fMS">vision</seg> &amp; that  <seg xml:id="C27_app1046-fMS">
