            <milestone unit="tei:p-START"/>
            <lb n="c57-0131__main__9"/>I</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C27_app1053-fMS">repassed</seg> in my  <seg xml:id="C27_app1055-fMS">memory</seg> my whole <lb n="c57-0131__main__10"/>life; my quiet happiness <seg xml:id="C27_app1057-fMS">when</seg> residing with <lb n="c57-0131__main__11"/>my family in <seg xml:id="C27_app1059-fMS">Geneva –The</seg> death of my  <seg xml:id="C27_app1061-fMS">Mother</seg>
         <lb n="c57-0131__main__12"/>and my departure for <seg xml:id="C27_app1063-fMS">Insgolstadt;</seg> I  <seg xml:id="C27_app1065-fMS">
