         <milestone unit="tei:p-END"/>
         <milestone unit="tei:p-START"/>
         <lb n="c57-0131__main__20"/>Ever since my recovery from the <seg xml:id="C27_app1083-fMS">fever</seg>
         <lb n="c57-0131__main__21"/>I had been in the custom of taking every <lb n="c57-0131__main__22"/>night a small quantity of <seg xml:id="C27_app1085-fMS">laudanum <lb n="c57-0131__main__23"/>
            <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c57-0131__main__d4e24388"/>a<del ana="end"/>
         </seg> for it was by means of this drug only <lb n="c57-0131__main__24"/>that I was enabled to gain the <seg xml:id="C27_app1087-fMS">
            <mod xml:id="c57-0131__main__d4e24393">
               <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c57-0131__main__d4e24395"/>sleep<del ana="end"/>
