            </mod>
            <w ana="start"/>necessa<lb n="c57-0131__main__25"/>ry<w ana="end"/> for the preservation of life.</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C27_app1088-fMS">O <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c57-0131__main__d4e24409"/>p<del ana="end"/> pressed</seg>
         <lb n="c57-0131__main__26"/>by the recollection of my various <seg xml:id="C27_app1090-fMS">
            <w ana="start"/>misfor<lb n="c57-0131__main__27"/>tunes<w ana="end"/>
         </seg> I now  <seg xml:id="C27_app1092-fMS">took a</seg> double  <seg xml:id="C27_app1094-fMS">dose</seg> &amp; soon <lb n="c57-0131__main__28"/>slept profoundly. But <seg xml:id="C27_app1096-fMS">alas sleep did <lb n="c57-0131__main__29"/>not afford me</seg>
