            <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c57-0131__main__d4e24440"/>to me<del ana="end"/>
            <lb n="c57-0131__main__31"/>a thousand objects that scared</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C27_app1103-fMS">me–</seg>
         <lb n="c57-0131__main__32"/>towards <seg xml:id="C27_app1105-fMS">mor <mod xml:id="c57-0131__main__d4e24447">
               <mdel ana="start"/>d<mdel ana="end"/>
               <add place="intralinear" xml:id="c57-0131__main__d4e24451">n </add>
            </mod> ing</seg> I was  <seg xml:id="C27_app1107-fMS">
            <del ana="start" rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c57-0131__main__d4e24455"/>opp<del ana="end"/> possessed by <lb n="c57-0131__main__33"/>a kind of</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C27_app1108-fMS">nightmare –</seg> I felt the  <seg xml:id="C27_app1110-fMS">fiends</seg>
         <lb n="c57-0131__main__34"/>grasp <seg xml:id="C27_app1112-fMS">on</seg> my  <seg xml:id="C27_app1114-fMS">neck</seg> and could not free <lb n="c57-0131__main__35"/>myself from <seg xml:id="C27_app1116-fMS">it—Groans</seg> &amp; cries rung in my  <seg xml:id="C27_app1118-fMS">
            <lb n="c57-0131__main__36"/>ears–</seg> My  <seg xml:id="C27_app1120-fMS">father</seg> who was watching over me,  <seg xml:id="C27_app1122-fMS">
